=head1 DESCRIPTION

The status of an Amazon Web Services Organization and the accounts
within that organization.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AccountStatusList => ArrayRef[L<Paws::NetworkManager::AccountStatus>]

The current service-linked role (SLR) deployment status for an Amazon
Web Services Organization's accounts. This will be either C<SUCCEEDED>
or C<IN_PROGRESS>.


=head2 OrganizationAwsServiceAccessStatus => Str

The status of the organization's AWS service access. This will be
C<ENABLED> or C<DISABLED>.


=head2 OrganizationId => Str

The ID of an Amazon Web Services Organization.


=head2 SLRDeploymentStatus => Str

The status of the SLR deployment for the account. This will be either
C<SUCCEEDED> or C<IN_PROGRESS>.



